<title type="html"><![CDATA[The Book “al-Rūḥ” – Did Ibn al-Qayyim Author it?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1499&amp;p=1600#p1600"><![CDATA[
<strong><span style="font-size: 200%; line-height: normal">The Book “al-Rūḥ” – Did Ibn al-Qayyim Author it?</span></strong><br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Reference:</span></strong> Salīm, ʿAmr ʿAbul-Muniʿim (2006), al-Masāʾil al-ʿIlmiyyah wa al-Fatāwā al-Sharʿiyyah Fatāwā al-Shaykh al-ʿAllāmah Muḥammad Nāṣir al-Dīn al-Albānī fī al-Madīnah wa al-Imārāt, First Edition. Ṭanṭā: Dār al-Ḍiyāʾ.<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Question:</span></strong> “You mentioned in your editing of the book al-Āyāt al-Bayyināt by al-Alūsī regarding the book ‘al-Rūḥ’ [The Soul] that there is doubt over its attribution to Ibn Qayyim al-Jawziyyah?”<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Response:</span></strong> “Yes, I have doubts regarding ascribing the book to Ibn al-Qayyim due to the numerous stories and rejected material it contains in addition to the fact that I did not come across a manuscript copy which can be relied upon to definitively ascribe the book to him.” P. 170<br /><br />Taken from: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.istiqaamah.net/the-book-al-ru%E1%B8%A5-did-ibn-al-qayyim-author-it/">http://www.istiqaamah.net/the-book-al-r ... author-it/</a><!-- m --><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=56">Shehzad Sattar</a> — Fri Jul 28, 2017 1:47 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
